\b Help and Logs
\b0 \
\
To view the KA Lite's application logs (for debugging or tracing), launch the `Console` application and filter by "ka-lite".\
\
You can view KA Lite logs in the `Preferences` dialog by clicking on the `Logs` tab.\
\
You can open `~/.kalite/server.log` to view access and debug logs of the KA Lite server.\
\
If you encounter issues, please file them at the [KA Lite Installers {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "repository%5D(https://github.com/learningequality/installers)"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 \ul \ulc2 repository](https://github.com/learningequality/installers)}} or at the [KA Lite {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "repository%5D(https://github.com/learningequality/ka-lite/issues/)."}}{\fldrslt \cf2 \ul \ulc2 repository](https://github.com/learningequality/ka-lite/issues/).}}\
